<placeName cert="high">Karanis&lt;Alexandria?</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Πτολεμαῖος Ἥρωνι τῶι υ<hi rend="diaeresis">ἱ</hi>ῷ χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="2"/>μέχρι σήμερον οὐχ εὕραμεν ἀγοραστήν. ἐκχωρῶ 

    <lb n="3"/>πάντα Διδύμῳ ἐπὶ τῷ λαβεῖν <hi rend="superscript">με</hi> <hi rend="subscript">τὸ</hi> τρίτον μέρος 

    <lb n="4"/>τοῦ δανείου καὶ τῶν ἄλλων. εἰ μὴ ὅτι συνεζήτηκα 

    <lb n="5"/>τῷ Πτολεμαίῳ πάλαι ἂν ἀπηλλαγμένοι <choice><corr>ἦμεν</corr><sic>ησμεν</sic></choice>· ὠργίσθη 

    <lb n="6"/>γὰρ <supplied cert="high" evidence="parallel" reason="illegible">καταβάς</supplied>. διὸ γράφω σοι ἵν᾽ εἰδῇς. ἀσπάζου 

    <lb n="7"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὰ τέ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>να σου καὶ <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">π</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">άντ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ας</unclear> τοὺς σοὺς καὶ Τά<hi rend="diaeresis">ι</hi>ν καὶ τὰ τέκνα αὐτῆ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ς</unclear>. 

    <lb n="8"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἐ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρρῶσθαί σε εὔχομαι</supplied>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="9"/>ἀπόδος Ἥρωνι ὁρι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">δείκτῃ</supplied>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.30512" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.30512" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="225" notBefore="201" type="textDate">frühes III</date></p></div><div n="meta.30512" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Mich.</title><biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">512</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">30512</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0163</series>; <biblScope type="volume">8</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">512</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0163;8;512" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.30512" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.30512" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="low" type="ancientFindspot">Alexandria</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.30512" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://wwwapp.cc.columbia.edu/ldpd/app/apis/item?mode=item&amp;key=michigan.apis.2298"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>